<SYNC Start=3584394><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3587918><P Class=KRCC>
산드라 탬플턴이야
<SYNC Start=3589895><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3592155><P Class=KRCC>
