<SYNC Start=674187><P Class=ENCC>
Ready?
<SYNC Start=675051><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=678024><P Class=ENCC>
And so the twins and I<br>
began our arduous journey...
<SYNC Start=681858><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=682061><P Class=ENCC>
...halfway around the world.
<SYNC Start=683961><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=684130><P Class=ENCC>
Unfortunately, there was no way<br>
to send a message back to America.
<SYNC Start=688590><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=688735><P Class=ENCC>
And so it was no surprise<br>
that the Army believed I was dead.
<SYNC Start=692694><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=708955><P Class=ENCC>
No, God!
<SYNC Start=711355><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=713092><P Class=ENCC>
After four months, Sandra had gotten<br>
over the worst of the nightmares.
<SYNC Start=717392><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=718231><P Class=ENCC>
When the phone rang, she didn't think<br>
it was somehow me calling her.
<SYNC Start=722065><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=722235><P Class=ENCC>
When a car drove past, she didn't<br>
get up to check out the window.
<SYNC Start=727070><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=762141><P Class=ENCC>
l talked with your father last night.
<SYNC Start=765201><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=768815><P Class=ENCC>
You never told me<br>
how your parents met.
<SYNC Start=771909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=771984><P Class=ENCC>
They met at Auburn.
<SYNC Start=773918><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=773986><P Class=ENCC>
What about the details?<br>
How they fell in love.
<SYNC Start=777786><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=777990><P Class=ENCC>
The circus. The war.
<SYNC Start=779890><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=780059><P Class=ENCC>
You never told me any of that.
<SYNC Start=781959><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=782128><P Class=ENCC>
That's because most of it<br>
