<SYNC Start=990498><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=990703><P Class=ENCC>
The other 90 percent is below<br>
the water where you can't see it.
<SYNC Start=994161><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=994340><P Class=ENCC>
And that's...
<SYNC Start=996331><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=996542><P Class=ENCC>
...what it is with you, Dad.
<SYNC Start=999306><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=999478><P Class=ENCC>
l am only seeing this little bit...
<SYNC Start=1002208><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1002381><P Class=ENCC>
...that sticks above the water.
<SYNC Start=1004212><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1004383><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, you're only seeing down<br>
to my nose? My chin? My--
<SYNC Start=1007477><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1007687><P Class=ENCC>
Dad, l have no idea who you are...
<SYNC Start=1010588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1010957><P Class=ENCC>
...because you've never told me<br>
a single fact.
<SYNC Start=1014085><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1014260><P Class=ENCC>
l've told you a thousand facts, Will.<br>
That's what l do, l tell stories!
<SYNC Start=1018458><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1018631><P Class=ENCC>
You tell...lies, Dad.
<SYNC Start=1022089><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1022168><P Class=ENCC>
You tell amusing lies.
<SYNC Start=1023362><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1023569><P Class=ENCC>
Stories are what you tell<br>
a 5-year-old at bedtime.
<SYNC Start=1026595><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1026973><P Class=ENCC>
They're not elaborate mythologies<br>
that you maintain...
<SYNC Start=1029635><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1030242><P Class=ENCC>
...when your son is 10 and 15<br>
and 20 and 30.
<SYNC Start=1032301><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1032478><P Class=ENCC>
And l believed you.
<SYNC Start=1035345><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1037183><P Class=ENCC>
l believed your stories<br>
so much longer than l should have.
<SYNC Start=1040516><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1040686><P Class=ENCC>
Then when l realized<br>
everything you said was impossible...
<SYNC Start=1043712><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1044090><P Class=ENCC>
...l felt like a fool<br>
to have trusted you.
<SYNC Start=1046217><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1046425><P Class=ENCC>
You're like Santa Claus<br>
and the Easter Bunny.
<SYNC Start=1048586><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1048761><P Class=ENCC>
Just as charming and just as fake.
<SYNC Start=1050592><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1050763><P Class=ENCC>
You think l'm fake.
<SYNC Start=1053095><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1054533><P Class=ENCC>
Only on the surface, Dad.<br>
But it's all l've ever seen.
<SYNC Start=1058594><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1060439><P Class=ENCC>
Look.
<SYNC Start=1062134><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1063642><P Class=ENCC>
l'm about to have...
<SYNC Start=1066133><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1066612><P Class=ENCC>
...a kid of my own.
<SYNC Start=1067738><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1068114><P Class=ENCC>
lt would kill me<br>
if he went through his whole life...
<SYNC Start=1070639><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1071017><P Class=ENCC>
...never understanding me.
<SYNC Start=1073144><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1073219><P Class=ENCC>
lt would kill you, huh?
<SYNC Start=1075517><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1077523><P Class=ENCC>
What do you want, Will?<br>
Who do you want me to be?
<SYNC Start=1081084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1081293><P Class=ENCC>
Just yourself.
<SYNC Start=1082988><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1083129><P Class=ENCC>
Good, bad, everything.<br>
Just show me who you are for once.
<SYNC Start=1086758><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1087133><P Class=ENCC>
l've been nothing but myself<br>
since the day l was born.
<SYNC Start=1090159><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1090336><P Class=ENCC>
And if you can't see that,<br>
it's your failing, not mine!
<SYNC Start=1094739><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1126238><P Class=ENCC>
Your father decided<br>
that he needed to have an office...
<SYNC Start=1130675><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1130843><P Class=ENCC>
...and, of course, it wouldn't do<br>
to have it in the house.
<SYNC Start=1134210><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1134280><P Class=ENCC>
So....
<SYNC Start=1135645><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1137383><P Class=ENCC>
You'll know better than me<br>
what's important.
<SYNC Start=1142047><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1152431><P Class=ENCC>
What is it?
<SYNC Start=1154490><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1156102><P Class=ENCC>
lt was during the war.
<SYNC Start=1158070><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1158204><P Class=ENCC>
Your father went missing.<br>
They thought he was dead.
<SYNC Start=1162072><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1163275><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, that really happened?
<SYNC Start=1165573><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1165744><P Class=ENCC>
Not everything your father says<br>
is a complete fabrication.
<SYNC Start=1169510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1170850><P Class=ENCC>
l think l'll go check on him.
<SYNC Start=1173819><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1176689><P Class=ENCC>
l need to lie down for a bit.
<SYNC Start=1178680><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1178891><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, go.
<SYNC Start=1181519><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1196408><P Class=ENCC>
After the war, the sons of Alabama<br>
returned home, looking for work.
<SYNC Start=1201311><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1201380><P Class=ENCC>
Each had the advantage over me.
<SYNC Start=1203143><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1203282><P Class=ENCC>
They were alive,<br>
while I was officially deceased.
<SYNC Start=1206718><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1206919><P Class=ENCC>
With my prospects few...
<SYNC Start=1208682><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1208854><P Class=ENCC>
...I took a job as a traveling salesman.<br>
It suited me.
<SYNC Start=1212654><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1212825><P Class=ENCC>
If there was one thing<br>
you can say about Edward Bloom...
<SYNC Start=1215885><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1216262><P Class=ENCC>
...it's that I am a social person.
<SYNC Start=1218389><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1219465><P Class=ENCC>
-Congratulations.<br>
-Thank you, sir.
<SYNC Start=1222491><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1223269><P Class=ENCC>
I could be gone<br>
for weeks at a time.
<SYNC Start=1225703><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1225905><P Class=ENCC>
But every other Friday,<br>
I put all the money I made...
<SYNC Start=1228806><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1229175><P Class=ENCC>
...into an account set aside<br>
for a proper house...
<SYNC Start=1232633><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1232811><P Class=ENCC>
...with a white picket fence.
<SYNC Start=1235143><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1240786><P Class=ENCC>
l'd like a moment of your time<br>
to tell you about my new product...
<SYNC Start=1244381><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1244557><P Class=ENCC>
...the Handi-matic.
<SYNC Start=1246787><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1262408><P Class=ENCC>
A few years later, I added<br>
other products and other cities...
<SYNC Start=1265605><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1265811><P Class=ENCC>
...until my territory stretched from<br>
the coast to western Texas.
<SYNC Start=1269372><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1294340><P Class=ENCC>
Edward?
<SYNC Start=1295705><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1295874><P Class=ENCC>
Edward Bloom!
<SYNC Start=1297535><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1297710><P Class=ENCC>
lt's me, Norther Winslow.
<SYNC Start=1299371><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1299545><P Class=ENCC>
l don't believe it.
<SYNC Start=1301410><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1301580><P Class=ENCC>
I was astonished to see the greatest<br>
poet of both Ashton and Spectre...
<SYNC Start=1305778><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1305985><P Class=ENCC>
...all the way out in Texas.
<SYNC Start=1307850><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1308020><P Class=ENCC>
l want you to know, when you left<br>
Spectre, it opened my eyes.
<SYNC Start=1311888><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1312258><P Class=ENCC>
There was a whole life out there<br>
that l was not living.
<SYNC Start=1315750><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1315928><P Class=ENCC>
So l traveled.
<SYNC Start=1317452><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1317663><P Class=ENCC>
l saw France, Africa,<br>
half of South America.
<SYNC Start=1320757><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1320933><P Class=ENCC>
Every day, a new adventure.<br>
That's my motto.
<SYNC Start=1323595><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1323769><P Class=ENCC>
That's great, Norther.<br>
l'm happy for you.
<SYNC Start=1325862><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1326038><P Class=ENCC>
What are you doing now?
<SYNC Start=1328404><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1329541><P Class=ENCC>
l'm robbing this place.
<SYNC Start=1331008><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1335281><P Class=ENCC>
All right, everybody down!
<SYNC Start=1337010><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1338617><P Class=ENCC>
Hey!<br>
Just slide that over.
<SYNC Start=1341814><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1348027><P Class=ENCC>
-Would you mind grabbing that?<br>
-What?
<SYNC Start=1350791><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1351864><P Class=ENCC>
The gun.
<SYNC Start=1352728><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1354867><P Class=ENCC>
l'm gonna be cleaning out<br>
the cash drawers...
<SYNC Start=1356698><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1356869><P Class=ENCC>
...and my associate here<br>
is gonna handle the vault.
<SYNC Start=1360999><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1367046><P Class=ENCC>
All right, you!<br>
You help my friend, okay?
<SYNC Start=1370538><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1371417><P Class=ENCC>
Let's go!
<SYNC Start=1372941><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1392705><P Class=ENCC>
l'm sorry, ma'am.<br>
l am.
<SYNC Start=1394605><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1394773><P Class=ENCC>
l really just don't want anyone<br>
to get hurt.
<SYNC Start=1397867><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1398043><P Class=ENCC>
lt's not that.
<SYNC Start=1399943><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1400946><P Class=ENCC>
lt's just....
<SYNC Start=1402880><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1408454><P Class=ENCC>
There's no money.
<SYNC Start=1409921><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1410789><P Class=ENCC>
We're completely bankrupt.<br>
Don't tell anybody.
<SYNC Start=1414657><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1414827><P Class=ENCC>
It turned out that the Savings & Loan<br>
had already been robbed...
<SYNC Start=1418786><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1418964><P Class=ENCC>
...not by armed bandits, but<br>
by speculators in Texas real estate.
<SYNC Start=1423526><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1423702><P Class=ENCC>
All right, let's go!
<SYNC Start=1425670><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1436849><P Class=ENCC>
Norther!
<SYNC Start=1438840><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1458570><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah! There's gotta be<br>
close to $400 here!
<SYNC Start=1461368><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1461507><P Class=ENCC>
And that's just from the drawers.
<SYNC Start=1463907><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1464076><P Class=ENCC>
Let's see what you got<br>
from the vault.
<SYNC Start=1466601><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1476555><P Class=ENCC>
This is it? The whole vault?
<SYNC Start=1479023><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1479191><P Class=ENCC>
l'm afraid so.
<SYNC Start=1481625><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
