<SYNC Start=2499811><P Class=ENCC>
...l realized l was in love with a man<br>
who could never love me back.
<SYNC Start=2504145><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2505216><P Class=ENCC>
l was living in a fairy tale.
<SYNC Start=2508185><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2508653><P Class=ENCC>
l'm not sure l should've told you<br>
any of this.
<SYNC Start=2510883><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2511055><P Class=ENCC>
No, no, no, l wanted to know. l'm....
<SYNC Start=2513615><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2513825><P Class=ENCC>
l'm glad l know.
<SYNC Start=2515156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2515960><P Class=ENCC>
l wanted to be as important to him<br>
as you were.
<SYNC Start=2519191><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2519831><P Class=ENCC>
And l'm....
<SYNC Start=2521628><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2522066><P Class=ENCC>
l was never gonna be.
<SYNC Start=2524466><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2527038><P Class=ENCC>
l was make-believe.
<SYNC Start=2528630><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2530074><P Class=ENCC>
And his other life, you....
<SYNC Start=2534977><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2535246><P Class=ENCC>
You were real.
<SYNC Start=2536804><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2561105><P Class=ENCC>
Mom?
<SYNC Start=2562732><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2563808><P Class=ENCC>
Josephine?
<SYNC Start=2565639><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2567812><P Class=ENCC>
Josephine?
<SYNC Start=2569211><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2582960><P Class=ENCC>
Will!
<SYNC Start=2584985><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2586130><P Class=ENCC>
What happened?
<SYNC Start=2587495><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2587632><P Class=ENCC>
Your father had a stroke.
<SYNC Start=2589224><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2590101><P Class=ENCC>
He's upstairs with your mom<br>
and Dr. Bennett.
<SYNC Start=2592661><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2592837><P Class=ENCC>
ls he gonna be okay?
<SYNC Start=2594065><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2602079><P Class=ENCC>
l don't suppose that l could...
<SYNC Start=2604104><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2604315><P Class=ENCC>
...stay here with him.<br>
l mean, in case....
<SYNC Start=2606840><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2607752><P Class=ENCC>
ln case he wakes up,<br>
l really ought to be here.
<SYNC Start=2610653><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2610821><P Class=ENCC>
l'll stay.
<SYNC Start=2612015><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2613090><P Class=ENCC>
Why don't you go home with<br>
Josephine. l'll stay tonight.
<SYNC Start=2616059><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2617995><P Class=ENCC>
-ls that okay?<br>
-Fine.
<SYNC Start=2620930><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2623868><P Class=ENCC>
Will, you'll call if there's any...?
<SYNC Start=2626769><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2626938><P Class=ENCC>
l will. l will. l'll call.
<SYNC Start=2629998><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2631676><P Class=ENCC>
-Do you want some time with Dad?<br>
-Yes. Thank you.
<SYNC Start=2635635><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2699777><P Class=ENCC>
Glad to see you're not trying<br>
to have a heartfelt talk.
<SYNC Start=2703178><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2706384><P Class=ENCC>
One of my greatest<br>
annoyances is when...
<SYNC Start=2708978><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2709186><P Class=ENCC>
...people try to talk to those<br>
who can't hear them.
<SYNC Start=2712087><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2712256><P Class=ENCC>
Well, we have an advantage.
<SYNC Start=2714315><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2714959><P Class=ENCC>
My father and l never talk.
<SYNC Start=2717018><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2723768><P Class=ENCC>
Your father ever tell you<br>
about the day you were born?
<SYNC Start=2726828><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2726904><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, a thousand times.<br>
He caught an uncatchable fish.
<SYNC Start=2730203><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2730374><P Class=ENCC>
Not that. The real story.<br>
He ever tell you that?
<SYNC Start=2734310><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2734679><P Class=ENCC>
No.
<SYNC Start=2736306><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2736681><P Class=ENCC>
Well, your mother came in about<br>
3 in the afternoon.
<SYNC Start=2740014><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2740184><P Class=ENCC>
Her neighbor drove her, on account of<br>
your father was away on business...
<SYNC Start=2744848><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2744922><P Class=ENCC>
...in Wichita.
<SYNC Start=2746389><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2747258><P Class=ENCC>
You were born a week early,<br>
but there were no complications.
<SYNC Start=2750989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2751162><P Class=ENCC>
lt was a perfect delivery.<br>
Your father was sorry not to be there.
<SYNC Start=2756862><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2757334><P Class=ENCC>
But it wasn't the custom then for men<br>
to be in the room for deliveries...
<SYNC Start=2762067><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2762273><P Class=ENCC>
...so l can't see how it would've been<br>
much different had he been there.
<SYNC Start=2766437><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2766811><P Class=ENCC>
And that's the real story<br>
of how you were born.
<SYNC Start=2769405><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2770147><P Class=ENCC>
Not very exciting, is it?
<SYNC Start=2772445><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2772817><P Class=ENCC>
And l suppose if l had to choose<br>
between the true version...
<SYNC Start=2776685><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2776821><P Class=ENCC>
...and an elaborate one involving<br>
a fish and a wedding ring...
<SYNC Start=2781224><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2781425><P Class=ENCC>
...l might choose the fancy version.
<SYNC Start=2783359><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2784161><P Class=ENCC>
But, then that's just me.
<SYNC Start=2786095><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2787164><P Class=ENCC>
l kind of liked your version.
<SYNC Start=2789155><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2811255><P Class=ENCC>
Dad?
<SYNC Start=2812882><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2815025><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, Dad? Hey, you want me<br>
to get the nurse?
<SYNC Start=2818461><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2820397><P Class=ENCC>
What do you want? What can l do?<br>
What can l get?
<SYNC Start=2823423><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2823868><P Class=ENCC>
You want some water?
<SYNC Start=2826234><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2826871><P Class=ENCC>
You want a bit of water?
<SYNC Start=2828270><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2831208><P Class=ENCC>
The river.
<SYNC Start=2833938><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2835412><P Class=ENCC>
The river?
<SYNC Start=2837277><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2837882><P Class=ENCC>
Tell me how it happens.
<SYNC Start=2841978><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2843921><P Class=ENCC>
How what happens?
<SYNC Start=2846788><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2846891><P Class=ENCC>
How l go.
<SYNC Start=2849223><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2853564><P Class=ENCC>
You mean what you saw in The Eye?
<SYNC Start=2856089><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2870147><P Class=ENCC>
l don't know that story, Dad.<br>
You never told me that one.
<SYNC Start=2873378><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2876320><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. Hey, okay, l'll try.
<SYNC Start=2879312><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2879523><P Class=ENCC>
l need your help.<br>
Tell me how it starts.
<SYNC Start=2882151><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2884428><P Class=ENCC>
Like this.
<SYNC Start=2888091><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2888265><P Class=ENCC>
Okay. Okay.
<SYNC Start=2890256><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2893003><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, so it's in the morning...
<SYNC Start=2896336><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2896540><P Class=ENCC>
...and you and l are in the hospital,<br>
and l've fallen asleep. And l wake up...
<SYNC Start=2900567><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2901178><P Class=ENCC>
...and I see you,<br>
and somehow you're better.
<SYNC Start=2904477><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2904849><P Class=ENCC>
Dad?
<SYNC Start=2906009><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2906083><P Class=ENCC>
You're different.
<SYNC Start=2908017><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2908986><P Class=ENCC>
-Dad.<br>
-Let's get out of here.
<SYNC Start=2911955><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2912122><P Class=ENCC>
Then I say;
<SYNC Start=2913316><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2913490><P Class=ENCC>
Dad, you're in no condition--
<SYNC Start=2914980><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2915159><P Class=ENCC>
Get that wheelchair.
<SYNC Start=2917457><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2920030><P Class=ENCC>
Hurry up! We haven't much time!
<SYNC Start=2922055><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2922132><P Class=ENCC>
Once we get off this floor,<br>
we're in the clear.
<SYNC Start=2924430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2924635><P Class=ENCC>
And we get in the wheelchair...
<SYNC Start=2926330><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2926503><P Class=ENCC>
-Faster!<br>
-...like we're escaping the hospital.
<SYNC Start=2929939><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2930140><P Class=ENCC>
What are you doing?
<SYNC Start=2932108><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2932176><P Class=ENCC>
We pass Dr. Bennett,<br>
who tries to slow us down.
<SYNC Start=2934371><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2934545><P Class=ENCC>
-Stop them!<br>
-We're flying down the hall.
<SYNC Start=2937480><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2937648><P Class=ENCC>
Orderly after orderly is chasing us.
<SYNC Start=2939582><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2940184><P Class=ENCC>
Mom and Josephine<br>
are at the end.
<SYNC Start=2942084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2942152><P Class=ENCC>
No time to explain! Stall them!
<SYNC Start=2945087><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2950494><P Class=ENCC>
We come flying out<br>
over the curb...
<SYNC Start=2952462><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2952663><P Class=ENCC>
...and your old red Charger is there.<br>
But it's new. Brand-new.
<SYNC Start=2957100><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2957268><P Class=ENCC>
And l pick you up...
<SYNC Start=2959498><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2959670><P Class=ENCC>
...and somehow you hardly weigh<br>
anything. l can't explain it.
<SYNC Start=2963333><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2967611><P Class=ENCC>
Leave it! We don't need it!
<SYNC Start=2970341><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2972449><P Class=ENCC>
Water. l need water.
<SYNC Start=2974883><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2978155><P Class=ENCC>
-Where are we going?<br>
-The river.
<SYNC Start=2980123><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2987164><P Class=ENCC>
And we have to take Glenville<br>
to avoid traffic...
<SYNC Start=2989530><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2989700><P Class=ENCC>
...because the damn church<br>
people drive too slow.
<SYNC Start=2992464><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3033344><P Class=ENCC>
And as we get close to the river...
<SYNC Start=3038509><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3047257><P Class=ENCC>
He's here!
<SYNC Start=3049384><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3049693><P Class=ENCC>
...we see that everybody<br>
is already there.
<SYNC Start=3052526><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3069113><P Class=ENCC>
And l mean...
<SYNC Start=3070546><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3072016><P Class=ENCC>
...everyone.
<SYNC Start=3073176><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3085629><P Class=ENCC>
lt's unbelievable.
<SYNC Start=3088359><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3089033><P Class=ENCC>
The story of my life.
<SYNC Start=3093766><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3101612><P Class=ENCC>
The strange thing is, there's<br>
not a sad face to be found.
<SYNC Start=3104513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3104681><P Class=ENCC>
Everyone is just so glad<br>
to see you...
<SYNC Start=3107275><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3108419><P Class=ENCC>
...and send you off right.
<SYNC Start=3110614><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3110821><P Class=ENCC>
Goodbye, everybody!<br>
Farewell! Adieu!
<SYNC Start=3116453><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3127805><P Class=ENCC>
My girl in the river.
<SYNC Start=3130399><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3201912><P Class=ENCC>
You become what you always were.
<SYNC Start=3204745><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3206483><P Class=ENCC>
A very big fish.
<SYNC Start=3208747><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3213891><P Class=ENCC>
And that's how it happens.
<SYNC Start=3216291><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3217794><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah.
<SYNC Start=3219591><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3222466><P Class=ENCC>
Exactly.
<SYNC Start=3224627><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3266743><P Class=ENCC>
Mom?
<SYNC Start=3268438><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3355432><P Class=ENCC>
The Lord is my shepherd,<br>
l shall not be in want.
<SYNC Start=3358595><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3358769><P Class=ENCC>
He makes me to lie down<br>
in green pastures.
<SYNC Start=3362500><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3362572><P Class=ENCC>
He leads me beside the quiet waters.
<SYNC Start=3365473><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3365642><P Class=ENCC>
He restores my soul.
<SYNC Start=3367576><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3367744><P Class=ENCC>
He guides me in the paths of<br>
righteousness for his name's sake.
<SYNC Start=3371703><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3372449><P Class=ENCC>
Yea, though l walk through<br>
the valley of the shadow of death...
<SYNC Start=3375612><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3375786><P Class=ENCC>
...l will fear no evil,<br>
for you are with me.
<SYNC Start=3378448><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3378622><P Class=ENCC>
Surely goodness and love will<br>
follow me all the days of my life.
<SYNC Start=3382854><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3429906><P Class=ENCC>
Have you ever heard a joke so many<br>
times you've forgotten why it's funny?
<SYNC Start=3434536><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3434611><P Class=ENCC>
And then you hear it again<br>
and suddenly it's new.
<SYNC Start=3438604><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3438815><P Class=ENCC>
You remember why you loved it<br>
in the first place.
<SYNC Start=3441909><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3443820><P Class=ENCC>
So he said he'll fight the giant<br>
who was 15 feet tall!
<SYNC Start=3446914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3447124><P Class=ENCC>
-No way!<br>
-Dad! That's right, isn't it?
<SYNC Start=3450582><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3450794><P Class=ENCC>
Pretty much.
<SYNC Start=3452022><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3452396><P Class=ENCC>
See? So he was a giant.
<SYNC Start=3454523><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3454698><P Class=ENCC>
That was my father's final joke,<br>
I guess.
<SYNC Start=3457064><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3457401><P Class=ENCC>
A man tells his stories so many times<br>
that he becomes the stories.
<SYNC Start=3463135><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3464708><P Class=ENCC>
They live on after him.
<SYNC Start=3466938><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3469413><P Class=ENCC>
And in that way,<br>
he becomes immortal.
<SYNC Start=3472644><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
</BODY>
